      "span_text": "These data have been combined with an extract from the electronic medical record (EMR), obtained through StaRR, the Stanford Medicine Research Data Repository. StaRR contains patient demographics and clinical data including ICD-9 (International Classification of Diseases, Ninth Revision) codes and medication records."
